<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/966152-i-just-read-a-commentary-about-our-new">I just read a commentary about our new Faux President with the title, &quot;Donald Trump And The Dictator’s Handbook&quot; which did not mention the book! That seems odd, but such is our upsidedown world. Who agrees this book explains the phenomenon of Frumpitude?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_966152'><a id="like_count_community_question_966152" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/966152?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11612989-the-dictator-s-handbook">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/966152-i-just-read-a-commentary-about-our-new">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/966152-i-just-read-a-commentary-about-our-new">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

