<span id="freeTextContainer17542109308104790555"><br/>Mesmerizing and essential. A simple (yet well researched and presented) far reaching work that clearly explains why despots continue to thrive, how and why democracies flourish and why foreign aid and debt forgiveness can be a bad thing.<br/><br/>Highly recommended.</span>

          </span>
