<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56269232-aftershocks"><img alt="Aftershocks: Pandemic Politics and the End of the Old International Order" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1617077334l/56269232._SX98_.jpg" />
